DESCRIPTION:To support you during the IT environment migration\, we are of
 fering regular Migration Support Calls.\n\n \n\nThese sessions are designe
 d to:\n\n✅ Provide guidance and background information on the migration\
 n\n✅ Share practical tips and best practices\n\n✅ Answer your question
 s live\n\n✅ Learn from real use cases and experiences from the community
 \n\n \n\n👥 Who should join?\n\nAnyone affected by or interested in the 
 IT migration – regardless of role or level of experience.\n\n \n\n \n\n
 🎙 Hosts:\n\nCarsten & Günter\n\n \n\n📅 Format:\n\nInteractive learn
 ing & Q&A sessions\n\n(Details on dates\, times\, and dial‑in will be sh
 ared in this channel.)\n\n \n\n👉 Bring your questions\, challenges\, an
 d experiences.\n\n \n\nOur goal is to learn together and support each othe
 r throughout the migration.\n\nWe’re looking forward to your participati
 on!\n\nCarsten & Guenter\n\n\n\n\n________________________________________
