 changshun.com.cn>   烦请将我和佳蕾放CC。❤\n\n \n\nBest Regards\
 ,\n\nLily Liu\n\n \n\n----------------------------------------\n\n \n\nDea
 r D Talent Team\,\n\n尊敬的D Talent团队，\n\n \n\nWe are pleased to 
 invite you to our upcoming Biweekly Group Learning Session. This session w
 ill provide an opportunity to review progress on the ongoing training cour
 ses\, discuss usage of Coursera accounts\, and track the training hours. I
 t is also an opportunity to align on upcoming tasks and course content.\n\
 n我们诚挚地邀请您参加即将举行的 双周学习会议。本次
 会议将为大家提供一个回顾正在进行的培训课程进展、
 讨论Coursera账户使用情况以及跟踪培训时长的机会，同时
 也是一个对接即将开展的任务和课程内容的平台。\n\n \n\
 n会议主持人：小组长\n\nMeeting Host：Group Leader\n\n \n\nThe me
 eting will cover:\n\n会议内容包括：\n\n*	Review of Coursera account
  usage and training hours.\n\nCoursera账户使用情况和培训时长的
 回顾。\n\n*	Discussion of upcoming tasks and course content.\n\n即将
 开展的任务和课程内容的讨论。\n\n*	Feedback and suggestions f
 or improving our learning initiatives.\n\n提供改进学习计划的反
 馈和建议。\n\n \n\nNo.\n\nSelected by Group\n\nTopics\n\nCategory\n\n
 1\n\n1\n\nEmployee Full Lifecycle Platform/员工全生命周期平台\n\n
 HR\n\n2\n\n1\n\nBuild BCZ‘s Own Digital Ecosystem/自有AI生态\n\nIT\n
 \n3\n\n2\n\nAI Best Parameter Recommendations/AI Best 参数推荐\n\nPPI\
 n\n4\n\n2\n\nAI Knowledge Assistant/AI 知识助手\n\nIT\n\n5\n\n3\n\nEqu
 ipment Full Lifecycle Platform/设备全生命周期平台\n\nMachine\n\n6
