 n\n4\n\nAI Product Anomaly Analysis/AI Recipe Auto Optimization/AI 产品
 异常分析/AI配方自动化\n\nQuality/PPI\n\n8\n\n4\n\nQuality Issues 
 - AI Smart Solutions/质量问题AI智能解决方案\n\nQuality\n\n \n\nL
 ooking forward to seeing you there!\n\n期待与您共聚一堂！\n\n \n\
 nBest regards\,\n\nBCZ Digital Talent Team\n\n \n\n_______________________
