 ing & Q&A sessions\n\n(Details on dates\, times\, and dial‑in will be sh
 ared in this channel.)\n\n \n\n👉 Bring your questions\, challenges\, an
 d experiences.\n\n \n\nOur goal is to learn together and support each othe
 r throughout the migration.\n\nWe’re looking forward to your participati
 on!\n\nCarsten & Guenter\n\n\n\n\n________________________________________
