 osts:\n\nCarsten & Günter\n\n \n\n📅 Format:\n\nInteractive learning & 
 Q&A sessions\n\n(Details on dates\, times\, and dial‑in will be shared i
 n this channel.)\n\n \n\n👉 Bring your questions\, challenges\, and expe
 riences.\n\n \n\nOur goal is to learn together and support each other thro
 ughout the migration.\n\nWe’re looking forward to your participation!\n\
 nCarsten & Guenter\n\n\n\n\n______________________________________________
